# Basic Information
name: docx-manipulation
description: "Create, edit, and manipulate Word documents programmatically using python-docx"
version: "1.0"
author: claude-office-skills
license: MIT

# Categorization
category: document
tags:
  - docx
  - word
  - manipulation
  - editing
department: All

# AI Model Compatibility
